{"tid":1144323,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有關浸大/港大中醫一問","createTime":"2019-05-08T04:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T13:17:29.000Z","uid":36844,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bd19ed14f4207fa61e245f4ae4b94855c375d2c4","tid":1144323,"uid":36844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:32:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟今年廿三<br />\n早兩年係HKU space讀咗中醫藥學高級文憑<br />\n然後係中醫診所做執藥做咗年幾<br />\n最近個醫師叫我不如去讀返中醫<br />\n我考慮咗一輪，都心郁郁<br />\n我就諗住下年報浸大或港大個中醫<br />\n就問吓大家，呢兩間嘅收生情況係點？<br />\n我就知道浸大收生個分係24.7，我就得17分<br />\n但中藥嗰個HD同出咗嚟做嗰年幾工作經驗會唔會有幫助？<br />\n謝謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8b5278b9d18076c0f3167d363f4e5d3530465f","tid":1144323,"uid":71508,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"讀中醫緊係上大陸讀啦"},{"pid":"ed14885c7f451d5bae7132a857a7e5fad9508b99","tid":1144323,"uid":36844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f8b5278b9d18076c0f3167d363f4e5d3530465f","tid":1144323,"uid":71508,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"讀中醫緊係上大陸讀啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:44:11.000Z","msg":"就係唔想上大陸先係香港讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4594395b3566ebb1cbdaa60f8d3c91ca2217b24f","tid":1144323,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"無問題，interview嗰陣講曬成本本草綱本內容就得。如果佢話點解dse噉低分，你答我識好多asso first hon喎"},{"pid":"a987f54068972b4e42730267b04a77edd368b258","tid":1144323,"uid":142575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:58:19.000Z","msg":"去研究下nonjupas"},{"pid":"14dc601b3be1504b256e7fdf3684ca53d9d385ba","tid":1144323,"uid":149178,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"完全冇幫助喎 讀書同做野2回事 入大學睇嘅係成績 尤其是港大 個個入